1991;;Kafka;;American;;Steven Soderbergh;;Jeremy Irons, Alec Guinness, Theresa Russell, Ian Holm;;mystery;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kafka_(film);;Set in the city of Prague in 1919, Kafka tells the tale of an insurance worker who gets involved with an underground group after one of his co-workers is murdered. The underground group, responsible for bombings all over town, attempts to thwart a secret organization that controls the major events in society. He eventually penetrates the secret organization in order to confront them.